From: Jianyong Wu <wujianyong@hygon.cn>
Subject: sched: Extend cache aware scheduling into topology aware scheduling

This series extends the existing cache-aware scheduling (CONFIG_SCHED_CACHE)
to be topology-aware, considering NUMA distances between LLCs when making
migration decisions.

Signed-off-by: Jianyong Wu <wujianyong@hygon.cn>
---

---
